---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import profilePicture from '../assets/Itay Lisaey Profile Cropped.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title='About Me'
  description='Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet'
  addtionalClass='flex flex-col justify-start gap-6'
>
  <header title='header' class='flex items-center space-x-4'>
    <Image
      class='font-bold text-sm rounded-xl max-w-[10rem]'
      src={profilePicture}
      alt='Itay Lisaey Profile'
    />
    <section class='flex flex-col justify-start h-full'>
      <h1 class='font-bold text-xl'>Itay Lisaey</h1>
      <p>Web Developer & Team Lead</p>
      <span>üåê Israel</span>
    </section>
  </header>
  <section title='summary'>
    <!-- <h2 class='text-xl font-bold'>Summary</h2> -->
    <p>
      I'm Itay, a developer and a software team lead based in Israel. With a
      passion for both backend and frontend development, I've cultivated a
      strong skill set in React, Typescript, NodeJS, CSS, DevOps, CI/CD and
      Azure Cloud.
      <br />
       Beyond technical expertise, I truly believe in maintaining integrity,
      honesty and professionalism in all aspects of work and life.
      <br />
       Currently, my focus extends to data engineering and system design, where
      I continue to grow and adapt to the ever-evolving landscape of software
      development.
    </p>
  </section>
  <section title='skills'>
    <h2 class='text-xl font-bold'>Skills</h2>
    <p>
      React, JavaScript, Typescript, Azure Cloud, Node.JS, Docker, MongoDB, Go,
      DevOps, CI/CD, GCP, Project Management, UI/UX Design, Motion Graphics,
      Vector Illustrations.
    </p>
  </section>
  <section title='experience' class='flex flex-col gap-4'>
    <h2 class='text-xl font-bold'>Experience</h2>
    <ul role='list'>
      <li class='exprience'>
        <h3 class='text-xl'>Software Team Lead</h3>
        <h4>Israel Defense Forces (Intelligence Corps/Home Front Command)</h4>
        <h5 class='text-slate-500'>December 2022 - December 2023</h5>
        <p></p>
      </li>
      <li class='exprience'>
        <h3 class='text-xl'>Web Developer</h3>
        <h4>Israel Defense Forces (Intelligence Corps/Home Front Command)</h4>
        <h5 class='text-slate-500'>April 2021 - December 2022</h5>
        <p></p>
      </li>

      <li class='exprience'>
        <h3 class='text-xl'>Graphic Designer</h3>
        <h4>Freelancer & Part time</h4>
        <h5 class='text-slate-500'>June 2019 - April 2021</h5>
        <p>
          <ul class='marker:text-slate-700 list-disc pl-4'>
            <li>
              Developed the production design and overall layout for
              advertisements, banners, products, brochures, and more.
            </li>
            <li>
              Designed graphics to meet specific promotional and commercial
              needs.
            </li>
            <li>
              Developed visually captivating logos, effectively representing
              brand identities.
            </li>
            <li>
              Created dynamic animated videos to convey complex concepts in an
              engaging and easily understandable manner.
            </li>
            <li>
              Worked with Adobe Illustrator, Adobe After Effects, and Photoshop
              to craft visual design assets.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <style>
    li {
      margin: 0;
    }

    li.exprience {
      padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
      border-left: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
      position: relative;
      padding-left: 20px;
      margin-left: 10px;
    }

    li.exprience:last-child {
      border: 0px;
      padding-bottom: 0;
    }

    li.exprience:before {
      content: '';
      width: 7px;
      height: 7px;
      background: #334155;
      border: 3px solid #334155;
      border-radius: 50%;
      position: absolute;
      left: -4px;
      top: 0px;
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
